## HARD CONSTRAINTS — NEVER VIOLATE

| # | Constraint |
|---|-----------|
| 1 | Single HTML file. No external files. No imports. |
| 2 | Zero external dependencies. No CDN. No frameworks. No Google Fonts. |
| 3 | Mobile-first. 75%+ traffic is mobile on 3G/4G. |
| 4 | Page weight < 600KB (excluding images). |
| 5 | `direction: rtl` on `<html>`. `lang="ar"`. |
| 6 | Order form IS the only conversion point. No external links except WhatsApp. |
| 7 | All editable text marked `<!-- [EDITABLE: LABEL] -->`. |
| 8 | Form data POSTed to GAS_URL via `fetch` with `mode: 'no-cors'`. |
| 9 | Countdown backed by `localStorage` — never resets on refresh. |
| 10 | Honeypot field checked FIRST before any form validation. |
| 11 | **NEVER write "توصيل مجاني" anywhere on the page.** |
| 12 | **NEVER show a shipping price anywhere on the page.** |
| 13 | Size AND Color REQUIRED before form submit — shake animation if missing. |
| 14 | Order summary shows ONLY product price — no shipping math. |
| 15 | 69 wilayas in dropdown + 1,541 communes cascade. |
| 16 | All CTA text uses feminine Arabic: "اطلبي" not "اطلب". |
| 17 | `COMMUNE_DATA` entries must NOT contain non-Arabic characters (no Chinese, English, symbols). |
| 18 | No duplicate commune names within the same wilaya. |
| 19 | Wilaya 59-69 follow Loi 26-06 (Jaridat Rassmiya No. 25, April 2026) order. |
| 20 | **Bundle pricing cards MUST show savings amount (not just %) prominently.** |
| 21 | **"Stop Desk" option MUST clarify it's office pickup (للاستلام من المكتب).** |

